longBusinessSummary: Hedera Group AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, provides personal assistance, staffing, and recruitment services for healthcare and social care sectors in Sweden. It offers staffing services for doctors, nurses, occupational therapists, midwives, psychologists, physiotherapists, and social workers. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
